Install
  Install ApacheSolr (e.g. with `brew install solr`)
  Install Scons (e.g. with `brew install scons`)
  Install npm: `curl http://npmjs.org/install.sh | sh`
  Run `npm install http://github.com/polotek/libxmljs/tarball/master`
  Run `npm install http://github.com/gsf/node-solr/tarball/master`
  Run `npm install http://github.com/kkaefer/lib/tarball/master`

Run
  * ApacheSolr (with Homebrew install): solr "`pwd`/solr"
    (Make sure to use an absolute path for the instance dir)
  * `node app.js`